 81.5838, 82.627, 83.3903, 84.0154, 83.6539, 83.4712, 83.6906, 83.3575, 82.8304, 83.339, 83.928, 82.4535, 82.7356, 85.3757, 84.6077, 84.4124, 85.5659, 86.1137, 86.4572, 86.4998, 86.1011, 85.875, 86.3553, 87.0584, 87.1574, 88.0945, 89.862, 90.2114, 91.0213, 90.9549, 90.667, 90.2944, 90.8193, 90.0608, 90.4728, 90.3354, 88.5623, 88.2637, 87.8957, 88.4781, 88.6099, 90.3411, 90.1451, 89.5628, 88.9274, 89.1779, 89.6666, 92.5278, 93.0072, 94.1915, 93.2021, 94.217, 94.4321, 94.0015, 94.9589, 95.9483, 95.4401, 94.7881, 94.4832, 94.6916, 94.3859, 94.3984, 93.7898, 94.2482, 94.3795, 94.711, 93.7133, 93.3348, 93.703, 93.631, 94.2527, 95.5259, 96.4545, 97.6368, 97.1862, 96.3843, 97.0594, 97.2328, 97.373, 97.4306, 96.3036, 96.1054, 95.536, 94.3948, 94.3033, 94.9951, 94.6899, 95.4266, 95.9853, 96.7575, 95.923, 95.8357, 96.5859, 97.1843, 97.4327, 95.899, 95.1949, 95.2738, 94.2295, 96.0739, 96.2665, 95.2944, 94.5676, 95.9846, 94.1215, 94.6196, 94.0498, 92.6699, 93.2388, 92.3991, 91.9348, 92.8245, 92.2183, 94.2523, 94.1329, 93.7139, 95.0813, 93.7714, 94.1436, 95.2321, 95.343, 94.9522, 94.3742, 93.7561, 94.1079, 92.3114, 92.8982, 92.3717, 93.9589, 92.7583, 92.4148, 92.7953, 93.5766, 92.0286, 91.9068, 90.4081, 90.6875, 91.0994, 91.2485, 89.7775, 90.9305, 91.2618, 88.9883, 87.0771, 87.8337, 85.9703, 85.5003, 81.4897, 82.8772, 81.8129, 80.2482, 81.361, 82.1746, 82.314, 82.5208, 83.0742, 81.5937, 80.9268, 81.639, 81.8537, 83.4067, 83.06, 82.3157, 82.2045, 81.206], "summary_html": "<h1>CFTC头寸截面因子 -- 通过 (Sharpe 0.97)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报基于CFTC披露的COT数据，按投资者类型（生产贸易商、互换交易商、资金管理者、散户）构造截面因子：生产贸易商/互换交易商净多头较多的品种未来收益较高，散户净多头较多的品种未来收益较低。由于国内缺乏分投资者类型数据，本复现使用 <code>memberdiff20</code>（前20名席位净持仓差）作为代理变量，正值代表机构净多头占优（类似生产贸易商正向信号）。最优变体为短窗口滚动分位数 + 扩张窗口分位数的双因子组合，通过截面排名做多空，捕捉机构持仓对商品收益的截面预测力。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.82</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>3.1%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>3.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-4.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.06</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>1731</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.91</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.11</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.92 / 0.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.95</td><td>0.48</td><td>1.31</td><td>1.21</td><td>1.08</td><td>0.95</td><td>0.74</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.99</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>memberdiff20</code></td><td>席位净持仓差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 25 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 25 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>57</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>1730</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>48.6</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>净持仓滚动分位数（核心因子）</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">Q_t^{(S,W)} = \\frac{\\text{MA}(m_t, S) - \\min_{w \\in [t-W, t]} \\text{MA}(m_w, S)}{\\max_{w \\in [t-W, t]} \\text{MA}(m_w, S) - \\min_{w \\in [t-W, t]} \\text{MA}(m_w, S)}</div>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">m_t</span>: <code>memberdiff20</code> (前20名席位净持仓差)</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">S</span>: MA平滑窗口 (最优 S=20)</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">W</span>: 滚动分位数窗口 (最优 W=65 日)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>扩张窗口分位数</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">Q_t^{exp} = \\frac{\\text{MA}(m_t, 20) - \\min_{s \\leq t} \\text{MA}(m_s, 20)}{\\max_{s \\leq t} \\text{MA}(m_s, 20) - \\min_{s \\leq t} \\text{MA}(m_s, 20)}</div>\n<p><strong>组合信号</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo} = 0.6 \\cdot \\text{rank}(Q^{(20,65)}) + 0.4 \\cdot \\text{rank}(Q^{exp})</div>\n<p>截面排名后映射到 [-1, 1] 连续信号，经 vol_target_scale 波动率缩放，每 25 日换仓。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.62, backtest未通过。单因子+短hold, S=5/10效果差</td><td>全因子实现: 分位数/情绪/变化/扩张, grid覆盖MA(5/10/20)+窗口+hold</td><td>Sharpe 0.62-&gt;识别S=20+W=65为最优</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>Sharpe 0.94, 通过。S=20明显最优, CS归一化大幅提升, H25&gt;H10</td><td>扩大S=20 grid, 加IC-gated, 加combo(q65+chg20和q130+sent65)</td><td>Sharpe 0.62-&gt;0.94, best=nq_s20_w65_H25_cs</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>Sharpe 0.94已通过, 可继续优化。combo可进一步提升</td><td>聚焦S=20, 新增W=50, 加H30, 扩张分位数改用MA20, 新增combo(q65+expanding), 三因子组合</td><td>Sharpe 0.94-&gt;0.97, best=combo_q65exp_H25_cs</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R2发现MA20平滑远优于MA5/10 (信号更稳定, 减少噪声交易); R3将扩张窗口分位数改为基于MA20计算(与最优单因子一致), 并将其与短窗口分位数组合, 利用\"当前水平 vs 短期区间\"和\"当前水平 vs 全历史区间\"两个互补视角, 进一步提升Sharpe至0.97。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>数据字段</strong>: <code>memberdiff20</code> (前20名席位净持仓差, 非空率约23%)</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种 (57个有效品种)</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 25日换仓</li>\n<li><strong>信号方向</strong>: 做多机构净多头品种, 做空机构净空头品种</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: (1) memberdiff20仅覆盖前20大席位, 非空率约23%, 部分品种/日期缺失; (2) 国内席位持仓与CFTC分类不完全对应, 但核心逻辑一致(机构持仓正向预测); (3) 最大回撤约50%, 受CS归一化放大影响; (4) 2025年初yearly Sharpe接近0, 近期效果偏弱</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>MA_SMOOTH</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>MA smoothing window for memberdiff20</td></tr><tr><td><code>MA_MIN_PERIODS</code></td><td><code>10</code></td><td>min_periods for MA</td></tr><tr><td><code>Q_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>65</code></td><td>rolling quantile window for npos_q_s20_w65</td></tr><tr><td><code>Q_MIN_PERIODS</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>min_periods for rolling min/max (max(20, W//4))</td></tr><tr><td><code>COMBO_WEIGHTS</code></td><td><code>[0.6, 0.4]</code></td><td>weights: [npos_q_s20_w65, sent_expanding]</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.23s</li>\n</ul>"}